episodes.title: Zachary Quinto, Shailene Woodley, Barbie Ferreira Get Ready For 'Cult of Love' on Broadway
episodes.description: Next up at Second Stage Theater is the New York premiere of CULT OF LOVE, directed by Obie Award-winner Trip Cullman. Watch in this video as the cast (including Zachary Quito and Shailene Woodley) tells us more about what the new play is all about!
